<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jake Dow-Smith | Choreographer of Space-Time</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/jake.css">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="starfield"></div>

    <!-- The Machine UI -->
    <div class="machine-overlay">
        <header class="ui-header">
            <div class="status-indicator">
                <div class="status-dot"></div>
                <span>Autonomous Designer Profile / v2.0.0 (Luddite_Stable)</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
                <button id="retro-toggle"
                    style="background: #333; border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;">[
                    TOGGLE_FRONTPAGE_2000_MODE ]</button>
                <div class="coordinates">LAT: 51.5074 N / LON: 0.1278 W / ALT: UK RURAL</div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <footer class="ui-footer">
            <div class="scroll-status">INDEX: JAKE_DOWSMITH_ARCHIVE</div>
            <button id="reset-engine"
                style="background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--ui-border); color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;">[
                RESET_LAYOUT_ENGINE ]</button>
            <div class="help-text">CHOREOGRAPHING ATTENTION & SCARCITY</div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <!-- Space-Time Navigation Machine -->
    <div class="timeline-scrubber">
        <div class="scrubber-handle">000</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Horizontal Dual-Axis Stage -->
    <div class="dual-axis-container">

        <!-- SECTION 1: IDENTITY (THE LUDDITE) -->
        <section class="section" id="identity">
            <div class="content-limit" style="max-width: 900px;">
                <h1 class="reveal-text" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Jake Dow-Smith</h1>
                <div class="emoji-cloud reveal-text" style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; opacity: 0.5;">
                    🚴 ⌨️ 🛠️ 🕰️ 📻 🌑 🚲
                </div>
                <h2 class="reveal-text"
                    style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    [ CHOREOGRAPHER_OF_SPACE_TIME ]</h2>

                <p class="reveal-text"
                    style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    "Websites are not flyers. They are playful machines, choreographing attention across the canvas of
                    space and time."
                </p>

                <div class="reveal-text"
                    style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem; max-width: 600px;">
                    <p>独立交互设计师 / 可能是卢德分子 / 时空导演</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">“他并没有追求复杂的前端框架或沉重的 3D 效果，而是通过对交互逻辑、心理暗示和空间隐喻的极致挖掘，将浏览器作为一个画布使用。”</p>
                </div>

                <!-- BIOGRAPHY TABLE PANEL -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-bio" style="width: 380px; top: 10%; right: 5%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">SPECIFICATIONS_B.1987</div>
                    <table
                        style="width: 100%; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; border-collapse: collapse;">
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ui-border);">
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">ORIGIN</td>
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right;">London (1987)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ui-border);">
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">FIRST_COMMIT</td>
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right;">FrontPage @ Age 13</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ui-border);">
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">LUDDITE_INDEX</td>
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right;">High (Loves Mechanicals)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ui-border);">
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">DIET</td>
                            <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right;">No Meat / Animal Products</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <div
                        style="margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem; border: 1px dashed var(--accent); font-size: 0.7rem;">
                        <span style="color: var(--accent);">[ MEMORY_FRAGMENT ]</span><br>
                        "13 岁那年，我用 FrontPage 做了第一个网站。那是一个关于自行车的网站。我骑了多久车，我就做了多久网站。"
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- BICYCLE PHILOSOPHY PANEL -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-bicycle" style="width: 320px; bottom: 10%; left: 5%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">FREEDOM_ENGINE / BICYCLE</div>
                    <img src="assets/jake_machine_hero.png"
                        style="width: 100%; height: auto; border: 1px solid var(--ui-border); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.5;">
                        "我热爱自行车的机械结构，它能简单纯粹地放大人类体能的输入。它是自由的助推器：极少的法律限制，没有追踪定位。"
                    </p>
                    <p
                        style="font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic;">
                        - 手工组装每一辆车 / 痴迷于零件的组合 / 终极逃跑工具
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 2: WORKS (PLAYFUL MACHINES) -->
        <section class="section" id="portfolio">
            <div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%;">
                <h2 class="reveal-text"
                    style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); opacity: 0.05; font-size: 15rem; pointer-events: none;">
                    TOYS</h2>

                <!-- Project: Rosemary Butcher -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-proj2" style="width: 420px; top: 5%; left: 15%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">PROJ_CHOREOGRAPHY / ROSEMARYBUTCHER.COM</div>
                    <img src="assets/rosemary_vibe.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                    <div class="project-title">Physicality of Time</div>
                    <p class="project-desc">双轴联动交互。当你纵向滚动阅读时，顶部的横轴（时间）在同步横移。这种设计将时间物理化了，感知舞者 40 年生涯的厚度。</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Project: Apossible -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-proj1" style="width: 380px; bottom: 10%; left: 10%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">PROJ_KNOWLEDGE / APOSSIBLE.COM</div>
                    <img src="assets/apossible_vibe.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <div class="project-title">Universe of Thought</div>
                    <p class="project-desc">拒绝列表式目录，使用 D3.js 节点网络。把知识变成了一个可以游荡的宇宙。用户不再是阅读者，而是探险者。简单的拖拽让平面信息产生了物理体积感。</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Project: soft.camera -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-proj3" style="width: 320px; top: 15%; right: 25%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">PROJ_SENSORY / SOFT.CAMERA</div>
                    <img src="assets/soft_camera_vibe.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <div class="project-title">Rhythm Capture</div>
                    <p class="project-desc">实验性相机。故意破坏了相机的清晰度，利用算法将实时画面转化为抽象的、柔和的色块和纹理。它不是在记录画面，而是在捕获环境的节奏。</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Project: b-gen-22 Interactive Module -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-bgen22"
                    style="width: 320px; bottom: 5%; right: 5%; background: var(--accent); color: white;">
                    <div class="panel-label" style="background: var(--accent); color: white;">PROJ_SCARCITY / B-GEN-22
                    </div>
                    <div class="generator-container">
                        <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem;">反向设计工具：生成设计命题</p>
                        <div id="brief-display">Initiate generation sequence...</div>
                        <button id="gen-btn" class="gen-btn">EXECUTE_GENERATION</button>
                        <span class="attempts-left">ATTENTION_CREDITS: <span id="attempts-count">30</span>/30</span>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.6rem; margin-top: 1rem; opacity: 0.8;">* 只有 30
                            次尝试机会。技术上的“简陋”迫使你进行更高强度的思考。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Project: Publish Something Online -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-proj4" style="width: 350px; top: 50%; left: 45%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">PROJ_META / PUBLISHSOMETHINGONLINE.COM</div>
                    <div class="project-title">Resource Library</div>
                    <p class="project-desc">经过精心分类和注释的知识路径。左侧标签系统 + 右侧资源卡片。一个教你如何发布网站的网站，本身就是最佳实践的示范。</p>
                    <div
                        style="margin-top: 1rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--accent);">
                        [ CATEGORIES: TOOLS, HOSTING, DESIGN, SPIRIT ]
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Small Project Cards -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-proj5" style="width: 250px; top: 10%; right: 5%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">PROJ_MINIMAL / PAULCALVER.CC</div>
                    <p class="project-desc">摄影师作品集。极简的图像展示，快速的加载速度。网页本身退向幕后，让摄影作为主角。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION 3: ARCHIVE (PHILOSOPHY & TRANSLATION) -->
        <section class="section" id="references">
            <div style="max-width: 1000px; position: relative;">

                <!-- Interview Archive (Draggable) -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-interview"
                    style="width: 500px; top: -10%; left: 0; background: #1a1a1a;">
                    <div class="panel-label">INTERVIEW_ARCHIVE / THE_LUDDITE_VOICE</div>
                    <div class="interview-text"
                        style="font-size: 0.85rem; height: 350px; overflow-y: auto; padding-right: 15px;">
                        <p style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">>
                            ON_SLOWNESS (关于慢下来)</p>
                        <p>"我的设计理念是向那些习以为常的数据驱动型设计发起挑战，**鼓励人们慢下来**。我鼓励浏览者去互动，不要担心如果没能立即呈现信息就会失去他们。"</p>
                        <br>
                        <p style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">>
                            ON_REPAIRABILITY (关于完全控制)</p>
                        <p>"我几乎总是从零开始构建代码。这很重要：我必须理解代码里发生的一切，我有能力在出问题时修复它。就像我的自行车，出了问题我能亲手修好。"</p>
                        <br>
                        <p style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">>
                            ON_THE_OLD_WEB (关于旧互联网的纯真)</p>
                        <p>"我怀念 2010 年以前的互联网。它被社交网络囚禁并拆解了。我是在论坛上长大的。搜索引擎曾能索引一切，而现在信息在私人网络里丢失了。"</p>
                        <br>
                        <p style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">>
                            ON_RESTRICTION (关于限制带来的成长)</p>
                        <p>"在工作中，我依靠限制而成长。帕金森定律说工作会自动膨胀占满时间，我深信不疑。我热爱那些能像玩具一样被成年人拿来玩的东西。"</p>
                        <br>
                        <p style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">>
                            ON_LANDSCAPE (关于 ViaMichelin 效应)</p>
                        <p>"我用一个叫 ViaMichelin 的 App，因为它有『风景路线』选项。它绕过高速公路，带你经过村庄和山脉。它给了你思考的时间，让你偶遇驻足点。"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- SIGNAL TRANSLATION PANEL -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-signal" style="width: 450px; bottom: 0%; right: -5%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">SIGNALS_AND_TRANSLATION / WANDA_DM</div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
                        <p
                            style="color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            [ THE_CASE_OF_WANDA_DÍAZ_MERCED ]</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                            "我喜欢将信号从一种形式翻译成另一种形式。由于耳朵更加敏感，你可以通过听图表来发现肉眼无法察觉的异常。Wanda Díaz-Merced
                            将天体数据转化为声音，发现了视觉上被忽略的共振模式。"
                        </p>
                        <div style="margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                            <div class="sonification-viz" style="flex: 1;">
                                <div class="bar"></div>
                                <div class="bar"></div>
                                <div class="bar"></div>
                                <div class="bar"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="flex: 2; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                <b>视觉：</b> 擅长空间与概览，容易“平滑”锯齿。<br>
                                <b>听觉：</b> 擅长频率与时间，识别节奏与瞬态。
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- LUDDITE MANIFESTO PREVIEW -->
                <div class="draggable-panel" data-id="panel-luddite" style="width: 280px; top: 10%; right: -20%;">
                    <div class="panel-label">IDENTITY_CORE / LUDDITE?</div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-style: italic;">"Maybe, I am just a Luddite."</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                        反对权威，反感追踪，渴望那种能在不踩刹车的死飞自行车上穿梭伦敦街头的自由。
                    </p>
                    <div id="manifesto-trigger"
                        style="margin-top: 1rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--accent); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem;">
                        [ VIEW_MANIFESTO.SH ]
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Voyager Drifting Node -->
    <div id="voyager-probe" class="voyager-node">
        <div class="voyager-label">VOYAGER_1_COORD</div>
        <div class="voyager-signal" style="cursor: pointer; pointer-events: auto;" title="??"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Luddite Manifesto Modal (Hidden) -->
    <div id="luddite-modal"
        style="display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95); z-index: 200; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem;">
        <div
            style="max-width: 600px; border: 1px solid var(--accent); padding: 3rem; position: relative; background: var(--bg-color);">
            <div id="luddite-close"
                style="position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1rem; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent);">
                [ CLOSE_X ]</div>
            <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 2rem;">THE_LUDDITE_MANIFESTO
            </h2>
            <div
                style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-primary);">
                <p>"We do not fear the machine, we fear the data that hollows it out."</p><br>
                <p>Efficiency is a trap. Optimization is a ghost. We refuse the seamlessness of the modern web as it is
                    the silence of the assembly line.</p><br>
                <p>Give us the friction. Give us the broken link. Give us the site that only works when the user stops
                    to wonder why.</p><br>
                <p>Build from zero. Build because you can fix what you create. Build to be free.</p>
            </div>
            <p
                style="margin-top: 3rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--text-secondary); opacity: 0.5;">
                [ TRIGGERED_BY_COSMIC_SIGNAL ]</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="js/jake.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Inline trigger for the manifesto since it's a new element
        document.getElementById('manifesto-trigger').addEventListener('click', () => {
            document.getElementById('luddite-modal').style.display = 'flex';
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>